dcterms:description: The Coupon-Purchase dataset contains discount coupons applied to online purchases. It includes data on 142 coupons for products priced equal to or below 200 price units that have been purchased by at least one customer. The dataset provides purchase rates and discounted selling prices.
dcterms:title: Coupon-Purchase Dataset

dcterms:creator: I. Chuang

dcterms:description: The edX-Course dataset contains enrollment information for 290 Harvard and MIT courses. It includes course participation rates and certification rates, which are processed to estimate participation and certification metrics.
dcterms:title: edX-Course Dataset
